What is this?
=============

Chat is an activity used to exchange messages with friends or classmates.
You can chat about a topic you are studying or you can share something private that happened in your life.

How to use?
===========

Chat is part of the Sugar desktop.  Please refer to;

* [How to Get Sugar on sugarlabs.org](https://sugarlabs.org/),
* [How to use Sugar](https://help.sugarlabs.org/),
* [How to use Chat](https://help.sugarlabs.org/chat.html)
